name: Steppjacke mit Federfüllung
description: This bimaterial jacket is made of fabric with a soft to the touch lining and a natural down filling. Its removable hood is held on with a zipper. The hem is adorned with an eye-catching faux fur and has a sewn in drawstring. Its design delicately accentuates the waistline. In the front it has two zipped inside pockets. The sleeves are finished off with an elastic band. The bottom hem has slits at the sides fastened with a popper.
